
taken from
https://github.com/zonque/simple-alsa-loop

to get list of audio interfaces:

 cat /proc/asound/cards

 ex.  1 [USB            ]: USB-Audio - Scarlett 2i2 USB
                      Focusrite Scarlett 2i2 USB at usb-0000:00:14.0-3.2, high speed


 device name is hw:USB




to run:
	loop [PLAYBACK_DEVICE] [CAPTURE_DEVICE]

	ie.
	loop hw:USB hw:USB


capture_client, from jack source code examples

jackd -dalsa -dhw:USB
jack_lsp